234
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:33,000
Gliding through the shadows came the walker in the night.

235
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:49,000
From off the moorland's misting fells came grendel stalking.

236
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:53,000
