241
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:15,000
while a baleful light, flame more than light, flared from his eyes

242
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:17,000
and his glee was demonic.

243
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:23,000
Mighty and canny, Hayalach's kinsman was keenly watching

244
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:26,000
