Grendel's whole grip beneath the soaring roof!

270
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:16,000
All gazed with joy and wonder at the arm of Grendel.

271
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:19,000
Its fingers stretched up to the high roof.

272
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:24,000
Where the nail should be were claws of steel, cruel spikes.

273
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:28,000
Men shuddered as they looked on it.

274
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:31,000
